import React from 'react';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom';
import Card from './Cards';



ReactDOM.render(
  <>
  <Card 
  imgsrc="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzA2NDkwNjAwMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTA2OTYzNjM@._V1_.jpg" 
  title="A Netflix Original Series"
  sname="DARK"
  link="https://www.netflix.com/in/title/80100172" target="_blank"  
  /> 
  <Card
  imgsrc="https://www.cinematyrant.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/breaking-bad-on-netflix-700x1050.jpg" 
  title="A Netflix Original Series"
  sname="Breaking Bad"
  link="https://www.netflix.com/in/title/70143836" target="_blank"  
  />
  <Card
  imgsrc="https://i.pinimg.com/originals/da/cf/7a/dacf7adf184e48076524688d0ee48dd3.jpg" 
  title="A Netflix Original Series"
  sname="Lucifer"
  link="https://www.netflix.com/in/title/80057918" target="_blank"  
  />

  </>,
    document.getElementById('root')
  );
